content:
I'm glad I could help you snap back to reality. It's easy to get carried away with fond memories of past vacations, isn't it? The Fontainebleau in Miami sounds like an amazing place to relax and unwind, and I'm sure you must have had a wonderful time there.

But anyway, back to your current trip in Chicago! I hope you have a great time at The Gage and enjoy the rest of your conference. If you need any more recommendations or have any other questions, feel free to ask!
